On a Thursday it was eight o'clock 'til eight. And on Friday it was eight o'clock 'til eleven. And on a Saturday it was eight o'clock 'til about twelve o'clock or
 twelve thirty. Well people didn't get their wages 'til - dinner time on Saturday - they had to do all their shopping at night time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 What did you have to do there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Take groceries out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Delivery boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 And you got two and six?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Two and six. And I never got that money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 What happened to that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 The grocers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Did you ever make any tips off the people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Yes, we used to get tips off -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 That was about the only money you had to spend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Your mother didn't give you any money - she couldn't afford to could she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 No, we used to get a penny.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 How long did you stick that job for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 I stuck that job 'til - about 19 - 1894. And we left home - I left home then after that. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 How old were you then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Be about eleven. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 You'd be about twelve wouldn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 You actually left home then did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 I left home then. I got fed up with them being drunk. See, she started drinking. I left home and I went to live wit
h me sister in Liverpool. And her husband worked in a sugar house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Where was the suagar house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 In Apple Street. In Vauxhall - corner of Apple Street and Vauxhall Road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Tate and Lyle's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 No. Crosfield's.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Did they have sugar in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Yes. Now it's an oil cake - Crosfields oil cake.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 What did you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 I was in the office - sample room - taking all the samples to Stanley Street. Liverpool.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 For Crosfields?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Crosfields, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 He got you a job then did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 He got me a job. I got nine bob a week there. I got threepence pocket money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Off your sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 What were your hours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Six to six.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Half day Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Half a day Saturday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 You didn't work on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 How long were you there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Ten years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Did you get any holidays there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 I went from the office into the works after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Did you have any holidays there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 No. No holidays. No. You never got paid for holidays. I was there ten years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 'Till you were about twenty-two?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10712183\charrsid9248556 Yes, an}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 
d I left there and went to a - had a row with me sister and I went to live with me other sister in Bootle. Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Still the same job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8143793\charrsid9248556 Still the same - the su}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 gar house, yes. I was there t
en years. And then they closed down. I was out of work for twelve months. Couldn't get a job anywhere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 What year would this be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 About 19 - 1895. After I were in the sugar house. I left there about - 1900. When they closed down. I left there abou
t - 18 - 97. I was out of work twelve months and - I'd never done any hard work before and I used to follow the rubber work up in Lytham - a reclaim factory. And I was on the canal bank one day and a fellow come out - he says - can you used a shovel? I sa
y
s, yes, I can use a shovel. I'd never used a shovel before. So he took me in, he says, I got in a wagon of coal. Some wagons was seven ton, eight ton, some was heavier. We had to throw it into the boiler house through a window. Well - I - I threw two wago
n
s out first day and - I couldn't get out of bed the next morning I was so stiff. And me hands was all blistered. The next morning I went to work, got in a wagon, I stuck the shovel in the coal - I couldn't lift it. 'Til I got going. Well I was there for a
b
out three weeks with him. I got used to it. And then in the boiler there was a tube burst in a boiler - the trimmer got scaled. So they asked me would I go in there. I said yes, I'll go in there. So I went in there and I worked all day on the coal and the
 boss in the boiler house says go home and get your meals for the night - come back. And I worked all night.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 What were the hours there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Half past five to half past five. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Half day on Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 All - no, all day Saturday. And some days Sundays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 What was the rate of pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Fourpence an hour. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Did you have any holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 How long were you there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 I was there - see - forty-three years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Forty-three years at the rubber place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 It became better didn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 
I got fourpence and hour and then - there was a fireman short and I got that job and I got fivepence an hour in that job. And then in - time went on - the '14 - we had the '14 war.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 That wasn't bad money - it was almost thirty bob a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 
That wasn't bad money. And - we had a lot of - a lot of - all the gang went in the Army. I couldn't get in the Army - on account of me ear. And - we had all sorts. We had niggers there. We had Spaniar}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid678858\charrsid9248556 d}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 s there, we had Italians there. 
And they were always fighting with the niggers. Yes. Well after that - after the '14 war we worked on Government work. After that the works closed down. I was kept on - clearing up and all that. Well then - I got stopped. Then I was out of work another tw
e
lve months. Couldn't get a job anywhere. We go to the Labour Exchange and - were giving green cards out. And - I asked the clerk, can I have a green card? He said, have you been in the Army? I says, no. He says, well you can't have one. You couldn't get a
 
job anywhere unless you had a green card. Well we used to get a - a pound a week for the two of us. Ten shillings each. Well - after that - were a job broke out in the rubber works. There was - broke everything all round the yard. To - if was a fair wind 
blew 'em all down. And the engineer asked me would I come and work there - give 'em a hand to get 'em up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 The same firm you were working for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Yes. Well stopped with 'em for - 'til they fixed - finished the job. Painted them and all that and then 
he - he said to me he says, there's a - a gas engine coming here. He says, don't bother coming to my house, he says, get there at nine o'clock when the pilot comes in with the goods. If you see any machinery on it he says start the next morning. So I star
t
ed and we got the gasses you know. And then he says - the rubber works is going to start up again. Well - he says, he'll start the next morning on the rubber works, he says, get a gang of men in, he says, and I want good workers, not dodgers. So I went a 
got a gang of men and we went and cleaned the boilers and got 'e, all ready, got 'em lit up and I had charge of the job after th}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid678858\charrsid9248556 a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 
t.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid678858\charrsid9248556 So you were a sort of f}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 oreman were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Until you retired?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 What were the hours there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 We turned round to six to six.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Is the firm still open?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 
No. When I was sixty-five the missus says, you're not going to work there any more. You've done enough. So at sixty-five I - left. We didn't pay into any pension fund or anything like that. I said to the boss, what about a pension?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 What did he say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 
He said, well, he says, I don't know, he says, I'll see the directors. I knew there was some of 'em getting pensions - that was retiring. Any rate, he says, don't bother coming down
 - he says, I'll send you word. Well they give me a pound a week pension. And I had that for about two years and then they - they give me thirty shillings and I had that for about twelve months and then I got two pound. Yes. Well they - they closed down a
nd - I got a letter one morning with about six pound in it and they said that the works was closing down altogether and that was the money that the canteen had made and they'd divided it between the pensioners. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 How long ago did that happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Year before last.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 You saw that factory develop didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 In fact you were the key man at that time weren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Yes. Oh aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Would you have preferred another kind of job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Did you serve an apprenticeship or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 No,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Did you belong to a trade union or professional organization?
