\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 She was fed up. Yes. That's what she said, when you're sixty-five you're going to get out of that place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 You put an awful lot of time in there didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 You were an exceptionally loyal employee weren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 And she saved up. And - when I was sixty-four she said another twelve months and you're getting out of th
at. And when I was sixty-five she says, tell him you're finished. Well I didn't like the idea of giving it up because I didn't know how we}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid678858\charrsid9248556 'd manage. So I - she says, we}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 'll manage all right, she says, I've saved money up. And I was surprised what she'd saved up. So - we -
