\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Hoddle Lane. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Did you go to church at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 We used to go to church now and again - after we was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11290146 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Not regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 No. Not regular.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 It was Church of England?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Aye. The time I'd finished work on a Sunday I didn't feel like going to church.
