\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Did the church run any temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 No.
