\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Did you see the teachers - you wouldn't have much to do with schoolteachers either?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Did you see many employers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 The employers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Who did they mix up with - who did your employer mix up with - did he mix with the men or did he have a separate group of his own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Well - he - they never mixed up with us. No. Only used to come in and walk around every - about every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Would he be considered an important man in the area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Most important man?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 The most important man round here - maybe the local vicar, the local pri}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid999345\charrsid9248556 
est or a big shopkeeper, a counsel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 or or somebody lik}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid999345\charrsid9248556 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 
 that - was there anybody like that in your area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 No, nobody. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 How about the doctor - would he be important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 Oh the doctor. That's we all -
