Well they'd all have to go and - to the Parish. And they used to give them - vouchers. Aye. For ten shillings or five shillings. You had to take them to the shop and get your groceries and - hand the voucher in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10976855 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 There was no family allowance then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9962819 WW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7622360\charrsid9248556 No.
